data.description: Home for sale by Mingus Park! Features 3 bedrooms with bonus room, big back yard with fruit tree and alley access for additional parking. Kitchen overlooks the back yard, laundry room on the main level, and big bright sun-porch on the front of the house. Home is tenant occupied and requires an appointment please.
